#, no-c-format
msgid "Cleared"
msgstr "Librado"

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:198
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is the total of all cleared and reconciled transactions in this "
"account. See <link linkend=\"details.ledgers.cleared\">this section</link> "
"for more information about the cleared and reconciled states of transactions."
msgstr ""
"ESte es el total de todas las transacciones libradas y conciliadas de esta "
"cuenta. Vea <link linkend=\"details.ledgers.cleared\">esta sección</link> "
"para más información sobre los estados librados y conciliados de las "
"transacciones."

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:206
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "This is where &kappname; displays the total balance of the account, which "
#| "is the sum of all transactions in the account. However, if you select "
#| "more than one transaction in the transaction list, this changes to "
#| "display the sum of the selected transactions. This returns to the balance "
#| "when only one transaction is selected."
msgid ""
"This is where &kmymoney; displays the current balance of the account, which "
"is the sum of all transactions in the account. However, if you select more "
"than one transaction in the transaction list, this changes to display the "
"sum of the selected transactions. This returns to the balance when no "
"transactions or only one transaction is selected."
msgstr ""
"Aquí es donde &kappname; muestra el saldo total de la cuenta, que es la suma "
"de todos los asientos de la cuenta. Sin embargo, si selecciona más de un "
"asiento en la lista de asientos, cambia para mostrar la suma de las "
"transacciones seleccionadas. Vuelve al saldo cuando solo hay seleccionado un "
"asiento."

#. Tag: title
#: details-ledgers.docbook:216
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Filter area"
msgid "The filter area"
